data.description: BACK ON MARKET DUE TO NO FAULT OF THE SELLER, BUYER TERMINATED DUE TO RENTAL RESTRICTIONS. METICULOUSLY MAINTAINED 5 BEDROOM/4.5 BATH ESTATE HOME IN THE WOODLANDS WITH A PRIVATE POOL AND LAKE VIEWS!    This home will impress you from the moment you enter the grand two-story foyer. Features Include: Side-entry Garage, Open Concept Floor Plan, Primary Bedroom on Main Level, Au Pair/In-Law Suite, Workshop, Generous Secondary Bedrooms, Formal Dining Room, Gleaming Hardwood Flooring, Updated Dine-in Chef's Kitchen with Oversized Breakfast Bar, Breakfast Nook, Bay Windows, Designer Cabinetry, Quartz Countertops, Stainless Steel Appliances, Gas Cooktop, Double Ovens, Deep Stainless Steel Sink, Custom Backsplash and Pantry. The sun-drenched two-story great room has direct views to the kitchen and boasts a stacked stone gas fireplace and decorative mantle. The spacious primary retreat houses a seating area, tray ceilings, dual walk-in closets, and en suite bath with vaulted ceilings, double vanities, soaking tub and a separate shower. Upstairs, the catwalk will lead you to three ample bedrooms with large walk-in closets and two full baths. Endless possibilities to utilize the terrace level, it's fully finished with a bonus room, exercise room, bedroom, bath, full kitchen, storage, and has private access from the secondary driveway. French doors lead to a secluded oasis, including a resort quality in-ground swimming pool with a Eco Smarte Ionize/Oxidize System and motorized pool cover and new liner, impeccable landscaping flanked by mature trees, low maintenance turf and a pair of outbuildings. Updates: New Roof 2020, Gutters/Gutter Guards/Soffits 2022, New HVAC Systems with Surge Protectors 2019/2020, Garage Door/Opener 2021, Replacement Windows, Foam Insulation Attic/Basement, Reverse Osmosis Drinking Water, RainSoft Whole House Filtration System, Surge Protection at the Panel Boxes. Currently zoned for the Whitewater School District which includes Inman Elementary School, Whitewater Middle School and Whitewater High School.  Conveniently located near Trilith Studios, City Center Park, Historic Main Street Fayetteville, Starr's Mill, shopping, dining and I-85! Located just 22 miles from downtown Atlanta and 17 miles from Hartsfield-Jackson International Airport. Click the Virtual Tour link to experience the 3D Walkthrough today!
